    Really should have a good assortment of logging for this project.....

    Ideally, have trace/debug lines scattered around too, which can be optionally enabled when more verbose log output is required.

Paths Page-
    The paths page, for PDUs, Should ideally copy the value to clipboard when clicked. Minor change, but, nice.

Node Rename-
    Should have a button/action which can be used to rename a node.
    Prob should show a warning to the user letting them know it may cause downstream impact to services consuming the data. But, renaming a node should be possible. And, the relationships should be updated automatailly as well.

